title: King Arthur's Knights: The Tales Retold for Boys & Girls
creator: Henry Gilbert
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of King Arthur's Knights: The Tales Retold for Boys & Girls, by Henry Gilbert. Read by volunteer readers. This book is an attempt to tell some of the stories of King Arthur and his Knights in a way which will be interesting to every boy and girl who loves adventures. (Introduction by Henry Gilbert) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
